response.original_title: Cover Night Plus : POP OAT Big Brother
response.overview: COVER NIGHT Live POP OAT - BIG BROTHER of Green Wave 106.5 FM, both artists who own the stage who came to debut Cover Night. The first live of the year, Pop Pongkul and Oat Pramote, went really hard, singing and playing new covers of songs. Plus, they threw jokes and bites at each other until the audience was in a frenzy. Breaking records with live viewers reaching tens of thousands.
